{"type": "article", "id": 40221, "title": "有了这套组件，黄辣椒也能改造成吹奏乐器｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-04-26T22:55:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 39895, "name": "Hang Bike"}, {"id": 16083, "name": "SHIFT"}, {"id": 27729, "name": "汇丰银行"}, {"id": 31694, "name": "HSBC"}, {"id": 39376, "name": "Duncan Shotton"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 88, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170426234712WNOfRkB0JEsXG3PH.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Player’s Pflute by Jia Wu</h3><p>除了中规中矩的乐器和音乐类玩具之外，我们可不可以通过别的方式让小朋友们的音乐体验变得更有趣一些？在中国设计师 Jia Wu 看来，生活中再平凡的物品也有着发声的潜力。为此她以几种笛子为原型，设计了这套名为 <a href=\"https://www.jia-wu.com/player-s-pflute\" rel=\"nofollow\">Player’s Pflute</a> 的模块化乐器组件，其中包括 4 种吹口、2 种打孔器和 1 个连接器。有了这些组件，小朋友们可以把胡萝卜、黄辣椒、水杯等日常物品改造成乐器，在进行发明创造的同时自由地探索音乐的世界。在今年的雷克萨斯设计大赛上，Player’s Pflute 成功入围了 12 强。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234832istljO2u5xKf37JG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234832hrk9xtXZn3q8WNwe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666316\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234831ARInQLhtC2jcM7Sr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.424682\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234831OQTIgr1FkKsiuD56.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.924370\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234832x6oHv251QwWM4UdN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666316\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Heart by Hang Bike</h3><p>在发现越来越多的人开始骑自行车通勤后，捷克的一支热衷于自行车文化以及室内设计的团队创立了名为 <a href=\"http://www.hangbike.com/index.php/en/home-1\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hang Bike</a> 品牌，决定为住在小公寓的人们打造一系列实用性和颜值兼备的自行车架。抱着“车架本身就足够美观”的设计宗旨，他们新推出了这款名为 Heart 的心形挂架，在没有放上自行车时，人们或许还会以为它只是一个墙面装饰。尽管极简的 Heart 给人一种过于轻质的印象，但它独特的形状能够保证重量被均匀地施加在墙面上，不用担心掉落的问题。Heart 的最大承重为 20 千克，你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.hangbike.com/index.php/en/heart-2\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买，售价为 133 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234909RI4QS9zol7Zyd13t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.798750\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234909s2h6kbe8EMGXr15d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704262349098ujgbLopIUZyXvYO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Planet Pins by Duncan Shotton</h3><p>这套忠实还原太阳系的迷你模型是英国设计师 <a href=\"http://dshott.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Duncan Shotton</a> 的作品，共包含 9 款大头针。其中的 8 个行星是在英国制作后送往日本由 Shotton 亲自涂装的，混凝土版的月球则出自 Shotton 的两位台湾友人之手。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/duncanshotton/planet-pins\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价从 22 英镑起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234928S3hc5MrZ10ko6BEW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.755814\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234927SDHptVbWcJn7mFwd.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.307031\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234926va8YQufXHMSGdKc5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.787209\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234925EIjd3ytng4z0lVWN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234926JeDUo683uTVjqiv4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.329070\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Tent Collection by nendo</h3><p>你有想过把帐篷放到桌子上是怎样的画面吗？日本设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">nendo</a> 为意大利家具品牌 <a href=\"https://www.cappellini.it/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cappellini</a> 设计的 Tent 系列给出了一个颇具卡通感的答案。内置照明系统的圆锥形帐篷可以根据需要旋转，随时调整开口面朝的方向，作为展示柜使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234957A3WvXP1bTBEU7yQ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234957pDw6gIKbtjGyxhif.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704262349577IsnikZDCLqfplcG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704262349587G1C5wFEfl6qt9H0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>HSBC bank card by Shift</h3><p>为了更好地传递品牌形象，汇丰银行（HSBC）决定将旗下银行卡的设计化繁为简，委托香港设计咨询公司 <a href=\"http://shiftpartners.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shift</a> 制定了新的<a href=\"http://shiftpartners.com/work/hsbc-revolutionising-a-global-cards-portfolio/\" rel=\"nofollow\">卡面方案</a>。在这套将于今年内在 30 多个国家推行的卡面上，汇丰香港中环总行楼下标志性的狮子像被处理成了具有立体感的像素风，再通过 20 种颜色组合区分具体卡片类型。新卡还采用了黑红两色的侧边，分别代表借记卡和信用卡。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426235043Q9LFKWeaq2OwlMnP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704262350445wB3KEmINYozlvA1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426235044v1uEOsT6i7Jfr5Km.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426235045KjuSqWItb3rEYGN9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704262350463q5NvoxEOiy076sr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Anamorphic Sculptures by Jonty Hurwitz</h3><p>我们都知道哈哈镜能呈现出物体的失真状态，假如情况反过来又会是什么样的呢？来自伦敦的 <a href=\"http://www.jontyhurwitz.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jonty Hurwitz</a> 就是一位热衷于“制造扭曲”的艺术家，这些看起来有些恐怖的雕塑是他通过软件计算和数码渲染后“倒推”得来的，只有将它们放在圆柱形的镜子前才能看见“正常”的版本。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234752AY3CxJI8NoV2SyeT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.510000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234750aBKMsFLzkWfmpjTt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234751yhfqwNF4J3PuzjHX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.727000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704262347513yEwULKjvCMTPOl1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234751xLpIDdyCeOGgQsYm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170426234751raIfqlxG89UHJ3p5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.531000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}